
Permanent TODO priorities:
- more and better examples
- documentation, commented code
====================================

Perl debugger interaction:
- source viewer as a long-running script
- step-by-step debugging capability
- capability to load for debugging Perl script from any location
- 'Save Page As' dialog to save debugger output in a file

Configuration:
- search for INI file in all standard locations on the supported operating systems
- check file paths to determine if they are absolute or relative paths
- more INI file options
- default values if INI file is missing or corrupt
- configuration interface using 'config' URL, HTML interface and, when needed, 'restart' URL
- more command line arguments for GUI configuration

Security:
- mandatory access control lists for Mongoose
- optional md5 control of all locally executed scripts

All locally executed scripts:
- dialog to select and execute scripts from any folder
- detect file type by reading the shebang line
- temporary folders

CGI-like locally executed scripts:
- non-blocking execution using signals and slots
- check for STDERR from scripts, if any - display message
- display 'Working...' page before output is ready

Long-running scripts:
- check if long-running script is not already started
- check for STDERR from scripts, if any - display message
- independent settings for main window and long-running scripts window
- 'Cancel' button to abort a long-running script at any time

GUI:
- working windows size settings on Mac
- Print Preview from context menu

Extensibility:
- Mojolicious support - run Mojolicious scripts using morbo or hypnotoad Perl web servers

Help:
- Configuration options explained
- Keyboard shortcuts listed
- 'help' URL

Connectivity:
- Whitelist of allowed web sites
- Easier configuration of a custom local web server started with the browser

Building:
- build script for command line compilation of the browser
- Debian package producing script
- windeployqt script for win32 deployment
- Qt Installer Framework configuration script
